description: All options are displayed from Scan Multibranch Pipeline Triggers Interval select
descriptionHtml: All options are displayed from Scan Multibranch Pipeline Triggers Interval select

testStage.description: All options are displayed from Scan Multibranch Pipeline Triggers Interval select

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Click on the 'Periodically if not otherwise run' button from the Configuration page
Open 'Interval' drop down select from the Configuration page
Get an options list from the 'Scan Multibranch Pipeline Triggers. Interval' drop down select
Logout from instance http://localhost:8080/
